                <head>Black Republicanism in Pennsylvania</head>
                <origin/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Pennsylvania Republicans in the Legislature voted to table a resolution
                    prohibiting racial intermarriage. According to the Spirit, this shows that
                    Republicans, despite protests, do believe in Negro equality. Gets blurry at the
                    bottom.</summary>
            </div>
